lead_paragraph: Reaching top of the world seems to agree with Angelique Kerber, who celebrated her ascension to the number one ranking with a 6-4 6-3 win over Caroline Wozniacki on Thursday to advance to Saturday's U.S. Open final.

headline.print_headline: Kerber Celebrates Number One by Reaching U.S. Open Final
